author: Reuters
title: Australia says all WHO members should support a proposed coronavirus inquiry
description: Australia has become as one of Beijing's most forceful critics over the handling of the spread of the coronavirus, with Mr. Morrison urging several world leaders to support an international inquiry into its origins and spread.
content:
All member nations of the World Health Organization (WHO) should support a proposed independent review into the coronavirus pandemic, Australia's Prime Minister Scott Morrison said on Thursday, further threatening strained ties with China.
